quote.p:
—an acceptable definition to be applied to air-launched cruise
                                missiles (ALCMs) in START (i.e., that only nuclear-armed ALCMs with a range in excess of 1500 kilometers would
                                be included in the Treaty’s limits);

(a) there will be a period of time during which both sides would
                                commit not to deploy defensive systems currently prohibited by the
                                    ABM Treaty;
